title: Malaysia Set to Hold Rate as Growth Stays Strong, Inflation Low
description: Malaysia is set to keep its benchmark interest rate unchanged on Thursday, as better-than-expected economic growth coupled with low inflation provide a buffer for policymakers to stand pat.
